        "setup": "Become an approved Rapid partner via [Rapid API partner application](https://partner.expediagroup.com/en-us/join-us/rapid-api). Then sign in to the [Partner Portal](https://portal.expediapartnersolutions.com/) and go to `Connectivity` → `API key` to obtain your Rapid API key. The docs note the key stays in restricted development mode until your site review and production approval.",
